==English==
===Noun===
'''veg*n''' (''plural'' '''veg*ns''')

#''(Nonce word):'' [[Vegetarian]] and / or [[vegan]]; a person who may either eat no animal flesh or eat no animal products at all.

===Usage===
Veg*n does not distinguish between vegetarian or vegan. It is likely to be used when the person being described is of [[indeterminate]] status.

===Adjective===

#Relating to vegetarians and / or vegans.
#Relating to vegetarianism and / or veganism.

===Etymology===
Derived from vegan and vegetarian and the use in [[computer language]]s of [[*]] as a [[wildcard]]

===Derived terms===
*[[veg*nism]]

